林鄭對警察公共關係科人員「勞心勞力」和工作成效表示讚賞。<br />\n<br />\n「好仔唔當差」口號過去半年不絕於耳，最新一期《警聲》又透露，「一直積極按照市場情況適時調整招募策略」的警隊上月在北京進行招募活動，針對在當地就讀的香港大學生，設置招募攤位和舉行分享會，其中分享會有約30名來自北京大學、中國政法大學及北京中醫藥大學的香港學生出席。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20200109/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200109%2F&d=eKFc4b3FQa1ReKUUeYtKdHWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=9c3e675b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200109%2F&h=e6866563\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20200109/</a><br />\n死不悔改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T14:21:31.000Z","msg":"最憎人講　＂高度ＸＸ＂　，呢Ｄ根本唔係中文。"},{"pid":"15323b8e9817b166e04d23048284741de4a1fbcb","tid":1818004,"uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2423e9720536eea6c9b2954d982d5e9572233755","tid":1818004,"uid":21545,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e60b5a5f440036a2fb05578ba38db584eee179de","tid":1818004,"uid":212626,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"f66406f1ade5695ac4072d78b95f4323015de02b","tid":1818004,"uid":21545,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T14:08:09.000Z","msg":"好仔唔當差」口號過去半年不絕於耳，最新一期《警聲》又透露，「一直積極按照市場情況適時調整招募策略」的警隊上月在北京進行招募活動，針對在當地就讀的香港大學生，<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔夠多武警？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T14:14:40.000Z","msg":"霉到要上去請人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T14:18:29.000Z","msg":"之前又話